=09=09=09=09July 12th 2001
=09=09=09=09From The Economist print edition =20
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09Market jitters
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09
